FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773288217
OL,3,CGovernment considering formal apology
OL,4,Cfor state's role in forced adoptions
OL,6,FSuccessive governments previously
OL,7,Finsisted that the state had no role in
OL,8,Fforced adoptions. An ITV investigation
OL,9,Ffound evidence that they were funding
OL,10,Fover 100 homes for unmarried mothers
OL,11,Facross England.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Children and Families
OL,14,FMinister Josh MacAlister said: "I do
OL,15,Faccept the state had a role; it's
OL,16,Fimportant we are honest about that.
OL,17,FThe case for an apology is powerful,
OL,18,Fand it is something the Government is
OL,19,Fconsidering."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
