CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773288217
OL,3,CGovernment considering formal apology
OL,4,Cfor state's role in forced adoptions
OL,6,FShe said a Government apology "would
OL,7,Facknowledge that our adoptions were
OL,8,Fforced and that they caused harm, and
OL,9,Fthat adult adoptees and mothers
OL,10,Fdeserve redress, and that recognition
OL,11,Fmatters to us hugely".
OL,13,FA report by the UK Government's Joint
OL,14,FCommittee on Human Rights (JCHR) in
OL,15,F2022 recommended ministers apologise
OL,16,Fto unmarried women who were forced
OL,17,Finto unwanted adoptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773288217
OL,3,CGovernment considering formal apology
OL,4,Cfor state's role in forced adoptions
OL,6,FThe then-Conservative government
OL,7,Fresponded, saying that while it was
OL,8,Fsorry "on behalf of society" for the
OL,9,Fway women had been treated, it did not
OL,10,Fthink a formal apology appropriate
OL,11,F"since the state did not actively
OL,12,Fsupport these practices".
OL,14,FThe JCHR at the time said the lack of
OL,15,Fapology was "disappointing".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
