FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773288217
OL,3,CGovernment considering formal apology
OL,4,Cfor state's role in forced adoptions
OL,6,FMacAlister said the practice "went on
OL,7,Ffor decades".
OL,9,FHe said an apology would need to be
OL,10,Fdelivered "by someone senior in
OL,11,FGovernment to reflect the gravity of
OL,12,Fwhat happened", adding that there was
OL,13,Fa balance to be sought "between doing
OL,14,Fthings right and engaging people
OL,15,Ffully, and the desire people have,
OL,16,Frightly, to move quickly".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773288217
OL,3,CGovernment considering formal apology
OL,4,Cfor state's role in forced adoptions
OL,6,FHe committed to work with campaign
OL,7,Fgroups on the content of any apology
OL,8,Fbut said the government will "want to
OL,9,Fmove quickly because of the age of
OL,10,Fmany of the people who have been
OL,11,Faffected" by an issue which he said
OL,12,Fhad done "huge damage" to "tens of
OL,13,Fthousands of lives".
OL,15,FCampaigners told MPs that, alongside
OL,16,Fan apology, more support was needed
OL,17,Ffor mothers and adoptees, including
OL,18,Ffast-tracking them for trauma-informed
OL,19,Fsupport as well as better access to
OL,20,Ftheir records.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
